Hollis' that was. And that wasn't very long because my grandmother died, you see, I was only there about a year, and my grandmother died so I couldn't - wasn't anywhere for me to go and - stay for the weeks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7566687 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 When you were at Lady Hollis' for a year did you come home at holiday times?
