\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7566687 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 When did they feed on dry biscuits, was that after the heart business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4158279 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 Yes. 'Cos she said, I'd got a fatty heart you see. But when I went to Lowestoft on
