a
id, come on, run upstairs to me, and I did, and when he - got up - when I got up there he sort of felt - he said, she's got no fatted heart, he said, don't starve the poor child. He said, she couldn't run up those stairs and have her heart not pumping. So
 I don't know, one doctor said one thing and one the other. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7566687 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 
