\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4158279 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 W
ell she never went - she was never out at night because it's too dark and - unless - of course this young - when she got this young fellow he used to be out - they used to be out a while but - never late because we were all to bed about half past nine. Yo
u see my father used to do his garden, he was very keen gard}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16646281\charrsid15876756 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 
ner and he had a lovely garden, vegetables and everything, my mother used to do the flower part, and - he used to always go to bed at nine, and he always got up at five in the morning and did two 
- hours gardening before he caught his - train to London, and he loved that. We used to have a flower show you know at - in the village and - every year and he used to win no end of prizes for all his - vegetables and that.
