Oh yes, she loved gardening, she - we had a sort of young farm there because she used to have chickens and ducks, and then when my brother came he had something wrong with him, I don't know what it was now, something to do with the kidneys and he had a
 goat. Well she kept goat for - he had to live on goat's milk for a long time, and so we had two goats actually, and then my father bought us a goat cart with a little - thing to put one goat each side you know, but we couldn't make - train them to do it,
 they all - turned it over, so -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7566687 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 Did she look after the hens herself?
