s there is in these cupboards. And so she said to us, now you go out for a walk, you don't want to sit here playing in this lovely weather, you go out and take a walk. When we came back she'd burnt the lot. I never f
orgot that, and I said, when I have children I shan}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16646281\charrsid15876756 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 
t interfere with their toys. But - well my sister and I were heartbroken honestly because - all the time we'd been out walking as - dutifully walking through the lanes we'd been talking about what we'd do
