 anything that was small, you know, that he was able to do, but I think we had decorators in to paint it every three years and that sort of thing. And - but apart from that I don't think - I don't remember anything going wrong with it. The man - the - the
 
man we had, he used to do all sorts of little repairs in - small ways, you know, if there was a leak in the - stables or anything like that he'd see to that. But - apart from that I don't think there was any - our poor old pony died before we moved, of ol
d age. We had a new one but we didn't have it for long because we moved and we didn't have one then, we sold it.
