\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4158279 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 Oh yes, she did all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7566687 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 She was really quite like a nurse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4158279 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 Yes. That's right, she sort of took us over pretty well - completely in that; respect. But of course - just before the war they - well 
when this one went we didn't have a another 'cos my mother thought that we were both - all at school and that you see then, so it wasn't necessary. So then we had to sort of do things more for ourselves and - cope when we were at home.
