\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4158279 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13448389\charrsid15876756 Oh we always went to bed about six. We always - come on, bedtime, and all that. My sister
